  "date": "2026-01-14",
  "notes": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\nauto;text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Cartographie des risques de\ncorruption - Compte-rendu d’entretien<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n <tbody><tr>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Date de l’interview<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"462\" style=\"width:346.3pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">14 janvier 2026 </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Nom de la personne interviewée<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"462\" style=\"width:346.3pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">LE FAOU Eric </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Fonction de la personne interviewée<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"462\" style=\"width:346.3pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Directeur Immobilier et moyens\n  généraux ; rôle lié à la sûreté OIV (officier de sécurité) </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Noms des personnes interviewers<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"462\" style=\"width:346.3pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">LASSAUGE Antoine ; LEZMI Sandra ;\n  LASAGNI Sandra&nbsp;; <span style=\"text-transform:uppercase\">Diboues </span>Karine\n  </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%\">1.Périmètre de responsabilités &amp; activités<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Département /\n     rattachement fonctionnel</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n     line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Direction\n      immobilière et services généraux”</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n      line-height:115%\"> avec <b>2\n      dimensions</b> : (i) immobilier ; (ii) services généraux. </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Couverture\n     géographique</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Historique\n      principalement France</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n      115%\">, avec une <b>prise de contact\n      progressive avec les filiales</b> (démarche en cours). </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Pour l’international : appui <b>très distant/épisodique</b> (ex.\n      petits bureaux à l’étranger, office manager souvent “intégré” à une autre\n      fonction). <b>A</b></span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n      line-height:115%\">gences commerciales en Europe et au Mexique, ainsi\n      qu’aux États-Unis</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n      115%\">, et des <b>centres de collecte</b>\n      (périmètres industriels). </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Organisation /\n     ressources</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Immobilier</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> : activité portée <b>seul</b> (pas de ressources dédiées)\n      ; appui “abondant” sur des compétences connexes (ex. juridique pour la\n      gestion des baux). </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Services généraux</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> : présence d’<b>équipes de services généraux dans\n      chaque grand site</b> ; support plus parcellaire sur les petits sites. </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Mobilité &amp;\n      travel</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> (missions\n      de Damien Brocard), incluant achats voyages, agences de voyages,\n      véhicules de fonction, et potentiellement événementiel. </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Missions /\n     objectifs</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Immobilier</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> : gestion des <b>baux</b> et sujets immobiliers du\n      groupe ; <b>assainissement</b> de\n      situations immobilières complexes (baux/occupation) et situation\n      désormais plus “saine/clear”. </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Services généraux</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> : gestion d’un portefeuille\n      d’activités “multi-services” et “multi-techniques” (maintenance bâtiments\n      tertiaires, services aux collaborateurs), et <b>travaux neufs</b>. </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Stratégie\n      achats/gestion</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">\n      : volonté de <b>concentration de\n      marché</b> (moins de fournisseurs) pour raisons d’achat, de\n      professionnalisation et de gestion (approche Facility Management). </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Sûreté OIV</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> : relations régulières avec\n      l’administration/autorités compétentes au titre des obligations liées à\n      l’OIV (instructions interministérielles, interlocuteurs au ministère de\n      la santé, etc.). </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Processus\n     opérationnels cités</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n     115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Achats / appels\n      d’offres / contractualisation</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n      line-height:115%\"> : ouverture d’appels d’offres avec les Achats, panels,\n      choix documenté et collectif. </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Exécution &amp;\n      paiement</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> :\n      contrôle de facturation, réception des travaux/prestations avant\n      validation/paiement ; responsabilité des managers sur la réalisation. </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Contrôles\n      “mobilité/travel”</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n      115%\"> : rôle de contrôle dans le flux d’approbation (ex. consolidation\n      kilométrage vs consommation carburant, validation de seuil). </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%\">2. Interactions avec les tiers en interaction / risques de corruption\n&amp; contrôles cités<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Typologies de\n     tiers identifiées</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n     115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Immobilier</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> : propriétaires /\n      investisseurs (et, en environnement locatif, interlocuteur type “property\n      manager / gestionnaire de tour”). </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Facility\n      management / agrégateurs multi-métiers</span></b><span style=\"font-size:\n      11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> (exemples cités : “Vinci Facilities”, “SPI\n      facilities”). </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Prestataires de\n      services récurrents</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n      115%\"> : nettoyage, gardiennage, restauration collective (restauration\n      partiellement “au CSE” mentionnée), etc. </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">PME / artisans /\n      prestataires ponctuels</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n      line-height:115%\"> : cloisonneur, électricien, etc. </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Conseil /\n      indépendants</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">\n      (prestations de conseil). </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Mobilité / travel</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> : agences de voyages,\n      véhicules de fonction (politique “chapeau” en cours d’harmonisation). </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Secteur public /\n      autorités</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> :\n      urbanisme/mairies (ponctuel, souvent via responsables généraux) ;\n      administration/autorités pour la sûreté OIV. </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Nature des\n     interactions / fréquence</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n     line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Interactions <b>nombreuses</b> via la <b>multitude de prestataires\n      multi-techniques/multi-services</b> et un niveau de sous-traitance\n      variable selon l’histoire des sites et maturité des marchés. </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Relations orientées <b>contrats/renouvellements, exécution,\n      qualité de service, gestion de situations conflictuelles</b> (ex.\n      pression sur qualité attendue). </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Sur le public\n      (urbanisme/mairies) : échanges plutôt <b>administratifs (mail/courrier)</b>, pas de relation\n      “client-fournisseur” au sens classique. </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Risques de\n     corruption évoqués/identifiés pendant l’entretien</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Situation immobilière\n      complexe</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> à son\n      arrivée&nbsp;qu’il a assainie (les baux sont désormais à jour&nbsp;:\n      c’est sain, compétitif et dans le marché.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Risque\n      “quasi-régie / marchés dormants”</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n      line-height:115%\"> : absence de remise en concurrence, prestataire\n      “installé”, augmentations annuelles sans contrepartie, surcoûts et\n      non-qualité ; cela peut aussi créer des <b>situations potentiellement propices à la corruption</b>. </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Avantages induits\n      côté fournisseurs</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n      115%\"> : avant, cadeaux d’entreprise, voyages/loisirs, visant à sécuriser\n      un marché ou éviter un appel d’offres (“souvenirs” d’il y a &gt; 20 ans ;\n      jamais eu de soupçons au LFB). </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Cas concret\n      rencontré </span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">:\n      proposition de “déjeuner” par un directeur d’agence d’un prestataire dans\n      un <b>contexte de tension</b> et de\n      risque de rupture de marché ; refus explicite. </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Manipulation/conflit\n      d’intérêts autour des AO</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n      line-height:115%\"> : risque discuté (favoriser un prestataire via\n      critères orientés / intervention amont) ; vigilance collective et\n      détection rapide en cas d’écart. </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Conflits\n      d’intérêts personnels</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n      115%\"> : cas historiques évoqués de managers/collaborateurs faisant\n      réaliser des <b>travaux à domicile</b>\n      par des entreprises connues “dans le monde professionnel”, avec le risque\n      que cela s’inscrive dans une logique d’échange (“obtenir quelque chose en\n      échange”). </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Secteur public</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> : la possibilité théorique de\n      sollicitations “douteuses” par des collectivités est discutée (corruption\n      passive), mais <b>jamais confronté</b>.\n      </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Filiales</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> : perception que les filiales\n      sont “moins sous contrôle” du groupe sur ces sujets, avec autonomie et\n      spécificités locales ; discussion sur environnement potentiellement plus\n      risqué (ex. mention du Mexique). </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Contrôles /\n     mesures de maîtrise cités (tels que mentionnés)</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Processus Achats\n      &amp; appels d’offres</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n      115%\"> : AO ouverts avec les Achats ; panel non décidé par une seule\n      personne ; choix <b>collectif</b> ; <b>grille de choix pondérée</b> ;\n      documentation et conservation des traces. </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Autocontrôle/collégialité</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> : collaboration Achats décrite\n      comme garde-fou, “on n’est pas tout seul”, détection collective d’écarts.\n      </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Contrôle\n      exécution/paiement</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n      115%\"> : contrôle facturation, réception des travaux/prestations avant\n      validation/paiement ; managers responsables du réalisé. </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Culture &amp;\n      refus des cadeaux</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n      115%\"> : évolution culturelle ; exemples de refus (ex. bouteille de vin).\n      </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Référentiels\n      internes</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> :\n      référence à la <b>politique Achats</b>\n      et au <b>guide cadeaux</b>\n      (mentionnés comme supports pour refuser des invitations/avantages). </span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Cas “non AO”</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> : mention d’un usage de <b>formulaire non AO</b> (ex. situation qui\n      s’est passée à Arras sur nettoyage). La situation historique à Arras est\n      complexe, avec des prestations locales à peine contractualisées (ex.\n      nettoyage base vie) : ce ne sont pas des achats normaux standards. Cette\n      situation anormale est en train d’être assainie. Pour le nettoyage, un AO\n      global va être réalisé. Sur Arras, il y a une forte évolutivité avec une logique\n      chantier. On va quitter cette zone et rentrer de plus en plus dans le\n      process classique.</span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkADE3NGU5ZmIxLTc2NDctNDBhMy04NDk1LTU3NjMxMzYzYzdkNABGAAAAAADwe9xAfilmQqx49rknxfe_BwALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAAAAAAENAAALUxuWdJbuQa1gtngdcN-XAABzyyLKAAA%3d\"></a><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Mobilité/travel</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> : contrôle dans le flux\n      d’approbation (km vs carburant ; validation de seuil).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>",
